        au!
        au VimEnter,WinEnter,BufWinEnter,TabEnter,FocusGained,CmdwinEnter * setlocal cursorline
        au WinLeave,TabLeave,FocusLost,CmdwinLeave * setlocal nocursorline
augroup END


